description:
Watch The Touch of the Master's Hand Full Movie on Vision Video 

The Touch of the Master's Hand is an inspirational and captivating film that speaks eloquently to the worth and potential of every individual. This film parable, based on the beloved poem by Myra Brooks Welch, illustrates why all life is valuable and that anyone can find renewal and begin again. Produced and directed by award-winning filmmaker T.C. Christensen.

Director: Tom Christensen
Starring: Dick Brown, Shaun Jolley, Earl Kevitsh,John Richards, Sally Swenson
